						               													<description>Do you have what it takes to become a&amp;hellip;Turbo G.E.M.? A Galactic, Expert, Miner! Climb into your spaceship and get ready to gather the most valuable resources before the other Galactic Miners. Pilot your 3D ship using your Turbo blower, watch out for passing meteorites, explore new planets and mine powerful gems! Race back to your 3D Mother-ship, exchange your gems either to upgrade your spaceship or get the most VPs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Go into Turbo mode and become a Galactic, Expert, Miner with Turbo G.E.M!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The modular game board consists of a 3D Mother-ship, 3 planets, 6 3D spaceships, gems, quests, asteroids and upgrades.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players set up the board in any way they chose, pick up a spacecraft and place it next to the Mother-ship.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then they grab some quests and on their turn, they get to blow their spaceship, moving it towards their goal. Their goal is to navigate their craft towards planets, mine gems and return them to the Mother-ship, completing quests.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;They can also sell the gems in order to buy upgrades for their ships (which attach onto their spaceship). These include tractor beams, bigger engines, more storage space or state of the art sensors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The space between the Mother-ship and the planets is full of asteroids that might hide power ups or danger!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when a player collects a set number of points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
